    <release version="0.8.8" date="2025-09-25">
      <description>
        <p>Interface improvements and bug fixes</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Update to Gnome 49</li>
          <li>Added a donation bar when starting the program for the first time in the system (can be disabled by creating a file during installation: ~/.config/.mangojuice)</li>
          <li>Improved graphical display of profiles</li>
          <li>Improved interface style</li>
          <li>Added the ability to add multiple variables using ","</li>
          <li>An improvement in vkbasalt is available for AppImage and the native package: the ability to select reshaders has been added. Vaddum has currently prepared a selection of reshaders that can be downloaded from the release</li>
